com.rhizospherejs.gwt.client.bridge
Class ModelBridge<T>

java.lang.Object

All Implemented Interfaces:
ModelExtractor<T>
Direct Known Subclasses:
JavaScriptObjectModelBridge, JSONObjectModelBridge, JSONStringModelBridge
public abstract class ModelBridge<T>
extends java.lang.Object
implements ModelExtractor<T>

A ModelBridge is responsible for converting a Java object representing a Rhizosphere model into a JavaScriptObject that the Rhizosphere javascript library can use. Since ModelBridge also implements ModelExtractor, it is also capable of the reverse process of extracting the original Java instance from a generated JavaScriptObject.

Apart from a few stock model bridges for generic cases (see JavaScriptObjectModelBridge), all model bridges will be code-generated to match the model types sent to Rhizosphere.addModel(Object).

Author:
battlehorse@google.com (Riccardo Govoni)
